</div>We're drilling in crazy places like miles under the ocean floor because it's the only place the dems will allow us to drill.  There's more oil a lot closer in, in a lot shallower water...in the gulf..off the east coast..off the west coast, yet no one is allowed to drill it.  If this leak had been in 500ft of water, it woulda been plugged the first day.<br />
