Get off oil...ok...let's build some nukular plants...oh wait..we aren't allowed to build those either.  <br />
<br />
I agree we need more/different types of energy.  Wind, solar, etc are just fine and dandy.  The problem is we need the oil NOW, and will need it for the foreseeable future, until someone invents a viable plasma or ion drive for cars/trucks/tanks.  How about we use our own and not potentially cripple our nation's defense by importing all of our oil.<br />
